https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/wyoP2WSamMHGDNakoQqpBHxtuc.jpg B'z LIVE-GYM 2010 "Ain't No Magic" at TOKYO DOME is a home video by B'z, released July 28, 2010. The video, released simultaneously on DVD and Blu-ray, covers the finale of B'z LIVE-GYM 2010 "Ain't No Magic" that toured in support of their seventeenth studio album MAGIC.
